  "title": "chore: migrates 45% connectors/widgets to TypeScript",
  "body": "Hey team,\r\n\r\nThis pull request aggregates all the stacked pull requests already tests/validated in isolation that migrate 45% connectors/widgets to TypeScript.\r\n\r\nRemember, we are now targeting the **master**.\r\n\r\nYou can check the remaining state of this mission here: https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/discussions/4407.\r\n\r\nPlease would be cool if you could checkout this branch locally, and test a typed built with your current projects with specific focus on: \r\n\r\n- breadcrumb\r\n- clear-refinements\r\n- configure\r\n- confirure-related-items\r\n- current-refinements\r\n- hits\r\n- hits-per-page\r\n- infinive-hits\r\n- panel\r\n- autocomplete",
